metadata.name: Sefton Stars
metadata.description:
Matariki over Mount Sefton. 

This was one of the best night Iâ€™ve ever had watching the heavens. Although, it was very very windy. I did manage to find shelter by the kitchen at Mueller Hut and took this photo. 

If you ever get a chance to hike to the hut, do it and stay overnight and enjoy one of the best night skies in the world.
